        <Parent_String>chimney components [300003944], chimneys and chimney components [300052129], heating and cooking architectural elements [300076657], architectural elements [300000885], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
